great support. amazing app. a must have.
most useful app ever

The best vet app out there. I use the beat counter spin-off app for almost every examination. The cri and K+ calculator is a must have. Work paying for it.

replyContent: The latest update should rectify this problem. If it doesn't please send us an email.

content: Brilliant App!
Great app.

Recently started working as a sole responsibility night vet nurse in a referral centre and I find this app very good, it's handy in those time where your in a rush or even to pre-calculate emergency medication doses if you have a critical patient in. Very handy and useful. Good job guys. It will be interesting to see the further development of this app and the direction it will go.
I used to love this app but it's stopped working the last week now and I'm wondering why I paid for something that refuses to do what it's supposed to
replyContent: Please get in touch if this is still a problem in the latest version of the app.

content: Need to add commonly used steroidal drugs, such as Prednisone for dogs& prednisolone for cats.
replyContent: The latest update includes many more drugs and will now allow you to add your own as well.

content: Not bad
Great resource for a clinical phase veterinary student such as myself.
This app is great. Very easy to use and very useful at work.  Thanks
So helpful at the clinic when I get rely busy and need to do things fast

Highly rated and very useful for emergency work especially. Concerns about drugs not available  not really valid as I don't feel this app is designed to contain a full formulary ( keeping the bsava formulary PDF on the mobile maybe an idea?) Rather it is designed to provide a full range of calculations that are needed in a daily veterinary environment. Working in a busy practice this helps a lot.I'd happily pay ten uk pounds for this app and it's a steal at two!!
My only real complaint/suggestion seems to echo what some have already said--we either need a way to add our own drugs to the list or have a longer list of drugs and dosages!  Keep up the good work.
replyContent: The latest update includes many more drugs and will now allow you to add your own as well.
